@node Contributing
@chapter Contributing
@cindex contributing

OwnSona is a single-user system that happens to be open source.
Contributions are welcome, with two priorities the project does not
trade away:

@itemize @bullet
@item @b{Vendor neutrality on the server side.}  No generative-LLM
calls in the request or write path.  The only vendor-coupled seam is
@code{EmbeddingProvider}.  Tool descriptions stay generic.

@item @b{Additive schema migrations.}  No drops, no renames, no data
rewrites inside a migration class.  The narrow exception is the
embedding-dim resize case documented in @ref{Embedding Migration}.
@end itemize

